We can drive straight in and take Shucheng

3
00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:07.500
In this way

4
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.300
We will no longer be rootless duckweed

5
00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:11.900
They have the strength to fight the long game.

6
