This Shucheng is difficult to attack

9
00:00:16.866 --> 00:00:18.000
heavily defended

10
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.733
Our north and south armies are only 100,000 people

11
00:00:20.733 --> 00:00:22.700
How to chew this hard bone

12
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:24.166
Since I dare to come today

13
00:00:24.166 --> 00:00:25.766
Nature is fully prepared

14
00:00:26.733 --> 00:00:27.766
You see here

15
